# Outreach Contact Surfaces

## Invariant

Contact detail (phone, email, mailing address) appears on **exactly one** surface per view.

Use `outreachContactPlacement()` from `frontend/src/utils/outreachContactPlacement.ts` before adding any contact UI.

| Surface | When |
|---------|------|
| `key_contact_card` | Key Contact card mounted (lg+ right rail **or** below-lg main stack) — single CC contact surface |
| `primary_task` | Open task exists **and** Key Contact card not visible — inline on first sorted task row via `OutreachContactInline` |
| `recommended_action` | No open tasks **and** Key Contact card not visible — inline under RA label via `OutreachContactInline` |
| Queue table | Compact subline only — `OutreachContactCallout compact` |

## Do not

- Import bordered `OutreachContactCallout` (non-compact) into Command Center components
- Add a standalone contact box above/below tasks separate from the task row
- Show contact in both Recommended Action panel and Open Tasks on the same page

## Do

- Embed with `OutreachContactInline` inside existing task rows or RA subtitle
- Extend `outreachContactPlacement.test.ts` and Command Center dedup tests when changing placement
- Pass `showOutreachContact` / `showOutreachContactOnPrimaryTask` from parent based on placement
